	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok im am a High Elf mage and now at lvl 13.  For the first 4 levels I didnt buy anything yet saved it all for spells.  Armor will come off of the orc pawns at lvl 2.  Ok from lvls 1-4 i went to newbie hunting grounds and killed anything i could till 4.  Bought my pet spells and my other spells.  I then went to orc lift and got bound.  DO NOT GO TO HILL YET.  Stay on road and kill orcs there till about 5 then you can stay there and solo or get a group on orc hill.  If you are not in a group you will probaly get trained and died or pull too many and die.  Do this to lvl 8 and run to felwithe to get spells.  Now head down to Nro.  Kill spiders and other mobs that con blue black or yellow.  Save spider silk and sell it or become a talior and make raw silk(25skill needed for raw silk)do this till 10 or 11 and then head to WC and kill williwisp grab all LS and GLS.  You can do the quest or sell them for some money(Quest gives same amount as selling but you have to go to NK)ok get lvl 12 hunting wisp and go to FP and buy spells or find a place to buy your new spells. At lvl 12 you have Ward summoned a 41dd spell that works on summoned mobs only so you go to lavastorm.  Great XP and loot and only some things arrgo.  I got lvl 13 in about 3-4 hours there.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
